 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Open the saved HTML file in your favorite browser (double click on the file, or right-click - and choose \"Open with\").</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://www.w3schools.com/html/img_chrome.png\" style=\"width: 635px;\"><br></p></div>','HTML Introduction',24,2),(30,'<p class=\"intro\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">In this chapter we will show some basic HTML examples.</p><p class=\"intro\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Don\'t worry if we use tags you have not learned about yet.</p><hr style=\"border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); margin: 20px -16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">HTML Documents</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">All HTML documents must start with a document type declaration:&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</code>.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">The HTML document itself begins with&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">&lt;html&gt;</code>&nbsp;and ends with&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">&lt;/html&gt;</code>.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">The visible part of the HTML document is between&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">&lt;body&gt;</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">&lt;/body&gt;</code>.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">Example</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"padding: 8px 12px; box-sizing: inherit; border-left: 4px solid rgb(4, 170, 109); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; width: auto; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !impor